---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About">
  <main class="sarva-main">
    <p class="sarva-section-label" style="text-align:center">About</p>
    <h1 style="font-size:3.25rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:2rem;text-align:center">Who's behind SARVA?</h1>
    <div class="about-section">
      <p>SARVA is a one-person passion project blending two obsessions: the numbers behind modern cricket and the what-ifs of history.</p>
      <p>I'm Sarvajith, a college student who started this blog in 8th grade for friends and family, and somewhere along the way it became something more serious. When I'm not writing, I play chess for fun and make music — keyboards and vocals</p>
      <p style="margin-top:2rem">
        <strong style="color:var(--sarva-text)">Sarvajith Aravind Venugopal</strong><br/>
        <span>Science student · Musician · Blogger</span><br/>
        <a href="mailto:sarvajith.aravind@gmail.com" style="color:#4a9eff">sarvajith.aravind@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
      <img
        src="/images/sarvajith.jpg"
        alt="Sarvajith Aravind Venugopal"
        width="138"
        height="143"
        style="display:block;margin-top:1.5rem;width:9rem;height:9rem;object-fit:cover;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--sarva-border)"
      />
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
